 role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531617\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531617\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rip1665702746090.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rip1665702746090.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rip1665702746090.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rip1665702746090\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Creating Persistence Data with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ulic /prep</span>\n</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rip1665702746090__creating_persistence_data_with_ulicprep_205967\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">When using the License Management utility (<span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span>) to activate and return licenses, you need to use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> command for certain license types to prepare your system for licensing. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> enables the creation of Sentinel persistence data which securely maintains licensing data.\n </p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"rip1665702746090__note_w2600ab1b5b1_w2601ab1b5_w2602ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Always run\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> as Administrator <span class=\"ph\">or\n            Root</span>.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rip1665702746090__topic_d44667e1_d44668e1_d44669e1_d44670e1_d44671e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d887283e70\">\n                  \n When to use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rip1665702746090__p_d68123e1_d68124e1_d68125e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> on Unix and Linux for all licensing actions.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rip1665702746090__p_d68126e1_d68127e1_d68128e1\">On Windows, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> with standalone licenses where indicated:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Standalone Licenses on Windows that need <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span>:</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__1\">\n Standalone License Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__2\">\n Activate license\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__3\">\n Return license\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__1\">\n                        Cloud-Served (clock tampering enabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__2\">\n<img alt=\"Required\" class=\"image\" id=\"rip1665702746090__image_izl_2gw_rvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Tick_mark.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__3\">\n<img alt=\"Required\" class=\"image\" id=\"rip1665702746090__image_xzy_fgw_rvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Tick_mark.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__1\">\n                        Cloud-Served (clock tampering disabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__3\">\n<img alt=\"Required\" class=\"image\" id=\"rip1665702746090__image_ogf_ggw_rvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Tick_mark.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__1\">\n                        On-Premises (clock tampering enabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__2\">\n<img alt=\"Required\" class=\"image\" id=\"rip1665702746090__image_fhw_ggw_rvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Tick_mark.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__3\">\n<img alt=\"Required\" class=\"image\" id=\"rip1665702746090__image_n2h_ggw_rvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Tick_mark.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__1\">\n                        On-Premises (clock tampering disabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5984e1_d5985e1_d5986e1__entry__3\">\n<img alt=\"Required\" class=\"image\" id=\"rip1665702746090__image_pdj_ggw_rvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Tick_mark.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rip1665702746090__p_d68129e1_d68130e1_d68131e1\">For network licenses on Windows, persistence data is created automatically when you install the Sentinel RMS License Manager. On clients that are connected to an RMS server which has a Grace-enabled license, persistence data is created automatically on the client.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rip1665702746090__p_d68132e1_d68133e1_d68134e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> only needs to be used for commuter licenses. In this case, run <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ulic /prep</span> on the local client machine.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rip1665702746090__p_d68135e1_d68136e1_d68137e1\">On Windows, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> with network licenses where indicated:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"5\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Network Licenses on Windows that need <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span>:</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__1\">\n Network License Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n Activate license\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n Return license\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__1\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n                        On local system (Client) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n                        On RMS server \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n                        On local system (Client) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n                        On RMS server \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__1\">\n                        Cloud-Served (clock tampering enabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__1\">\n                        Cloud-Served (clock tampering disabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Commuter only</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__1\">\n                        On-Premises (clock tampering enabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__1\">\n                        On-Premises (clock tampering disabled) \n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\">\n Commuter only\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rip1665702746090__table_d5987e1_d5988e1_d5989e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rip1665702746090__p_d68138e1_d68139e1_d68140e1\">For Cloud LM Licensing, always use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> for all licensing actions.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"rip1665702746090__note_qnk_h4w_rvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> must be run as a single command. Run\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulic</span> with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/prep</span> only before performing your\n            next action.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgt1690346679212.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface License Management Utility (ulic)</a><p>The Uniface License Management utility (ulic) is responsible for activating and downloading required Sentinel licenses, for checking out licenses, and renewing the lease on licenses on a regular basis. The licenses themselves are maintained by the Sentinel Cloud Server.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531617\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531617\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Creating Persistence Data with ulic /prep Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Creating Persistence Data with ulic /prep When using the License Management utility ( ulic ) to activate and return licenses, you need to use the /prep command for certain license types to prepare your system for licensing. /prep enables the creation of Sentinel persistence data which securely maintains licensing data. Note: Always run /prep as Administrator or Root . When to use /prep Use /prep on Unix and Linux for all licensing actions. On Windows, use /prep with standalone licenses where indicated: Table 1. Standalone Licenses on Windows that need /prep : Standalone License Type Activate license Return license Cloud-Served (clock tampering enabled) Cloud-Served (clock tampering disabled) On-Premises (clock tampering enabled) On-Premises (clock tampering disabled) For network licenses on Windows, persistence data is created automatically when you install the Sentinel RMS License Manager. On clients that are connected to an RMS server which has a Grace-enabled license, persistence data is created automatically on the client. /prep only needs to be used for commuter licenses. In this case, run ulic /prep on the local client machine. On Windows, use /prep with network licenses where indicated: Table 2. Network Licenses on Windows that need /prep : Network License Type Activate license Return license On local system (Client) On RMS server On local system (Client) On RMS server Cloud-Served (clock tampering enabled) Commuter only Commuter only Cloud-Served (clock tampering disabled) Commuter only Commuter only On-Premises (clock tampering enabled) Commuter only Commuter only On-Premises (clock tampering disabled) Commuter only Commuter only For Cloud LM Licensing, always use /prep for all licensing actions. Note: /prep must be run as a single command. Run ulic with /prep only before performing your next action. Related Links Uniface License Management Utility (ulic) The Uniface License Management utility (ulic) is responsible for activating and downloading required Sentinel licenses, for checking out licenses, and renewing the lease on licenses on a regular basis. The licenses themselves are maintained by the Sentinel Cloud Server. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}